title: Isabelle Kormos
text:
Hi! Welcome to my website, I hope you are having a wonderful day! My name is Bella Kormos, and I am a third year student at University of California, Santa Barbara. I love traveling, being in nature, playing volleyball, doing yoga, wheel-throwing, and backpacking.
